---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import PremiumBadge from '../components/PremiumBadge';
---

<Layout
  title="Why Premium Cat Litter Matters"
  description="Discover the science behind premium cat litter. Learn why quality ingredients, superior formulations, and advanced technology make a real difference for your cat's health and comfort."
  ogImage="https://allnaturalcatlitter.com/og-why-premium.svg"
>
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <PremiumBadge client:load variant="gold">The Premium Promise</PremiumBadge>
      <h1>Why Premium<br /><span class="gradient-text">Makes the Difference</span></h1>
      <p class="page-hero__subtitle">
        The choice between standard and premium litter isn't about luxury—it's about
        your cat's health, comfort, and your peace of mind.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Science Section -->
  <section class="science section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="content-grid">
        <div class="content-main">
          <h2>The Science of Superior Litter</h2>
          <p>
            Premium cat litter isn't just marketing—it's material science at work. The difference
            lies in carefully selected ingredients, advanced manufacturing processes, and rigorous
            quality control that budget brands simply can't match.
          </p>
          <p>
            When you invest in premium litter, you're investing in technology developed specifically
            to address the unique challenges of odor control, moisture management, and feline comfort.
          </p>

          <h3>Molecular Odor Control</h3>
          <p>
            Standard litters mask odors with perfumes. Premium formulations attack odor at the
            molecular level using activated charcoal, natural zeolites, and enzymatic compounds
            that break down ammonia and other volatile compounds before they can reach your nose.
          </p>

          <h3>Superior Clumping Technology</h3>
          <p>
            The clumping action in premium litters happens faster and forms tighter bonds. This
            means less litter sticks to your scoop, the litter box stays cleaner between changes,
            and you use less product overall—making premium options more economical than they first appear.
          </p>

          <h3>Dust-Free Formulations</h3>
          <p>
            Airborne dust is a respiratory concern for both cats and humans. Premium litters undergo
            additional processing to remove fine particles, resulting in 99% dust-free products that
            are gentler on sensitive respiratory systems.
          </p>
        </div>

        <aside class="content-sidebar">
          <div class="info-card">
            <div class="info-card__icon">&#128200;</div>
            <h4>By The Numbers</h4>
            <ul class="stats-list">
              <li>
                <span class="stats-list__value">94%</span>
                <span class="stats-list__label">better odor neutralization</span>
              </li>
              <li>
                <span class="stats-list__value">3x</span>
                <span class="stats-list__label">longer between changes</span>
              </li>
              <li>
                <span class="stats-list__value">99%</span>
                <span class="stats-list__label">dust-free formula</span>
              </li>
              <li>
                <span class="stats-list__value">40%</span>
                <span class="stats-list__label">less tracking</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </aside>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Health Benefits -->
  <section class="health section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header text-center">
        <h2>Health Benefits for Your Cat</h2>
        <p class="section-subtitle">
          Premium litter isn't just about convenience—it's about creating a healthier
          environment for your feline companion.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="benefits-grid">
        <div class="benefit-card">
          <div class="benefit-card__icon">&#128576;</div>
          <h3>Respiratory Health</h3>
          <p>
            Dust-free formulas protect sensitive airways. Essential for kittens,
            seniors, and cats with asthma or allergies.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="benefit-card">
          <div class="benefit-card__icon">&#128062;</div>
          <h3>Paw Comfort</h3>
          <p>
            Softer, finer granules are gentler on paw pads. Especially important
            after declawing or for cats with sensitive feet.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="benefit-card">
          <div class="benefit-card__icon">&#128150;</div>
          <h3>Stress Reduction</h3>
          <p>
            A cleaner, fresher litter box encourages regular use, preventing
            stress-related elimination issues and UTIs.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="benefit-card">
          <div class="benefit-card__icon">&#127807;</div>
          <h3>Natural Ingredients</h3>
          <p>
            Premium brands avoid artificial fragrances and chemicals that can
            irritate sensitive cats or cause allergic reactions.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Cost Analysis -->
  <section class="cost section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="cost__content">
        <h2>The True Cost of Premium</h2>
        <p>
          While premium litter has a higher upfront cost per bag, the math often
          works out in your favor:
        </p>

        <div class="cost-comparison">
          <div class="cost-item">
            <h4>Standard Litter</h4>
            <div class="cost-item__details">
              <div class="cost-item__row">
                <span>Price per bag</span>
                <span>$8-12</span>
              </div>
              <div class="cost-item__row">
                <span>Lasts approximately</span>
                <span>1-2 weeks</span>
              </div>
              <div class="cost-item__row">
                <span>Monthly cost</span>
                <span>$16-48</span>
              </div>
              <div class="cost-item__row cost-item__row--total">
                <span>Annual cost</span>
                <span>$192-576</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="cost-item cost-item--premium">
            <h4>Premium Litter</h4>
            <div class="cost-item__details">
              <div class="cost-item__row">
                <span>Price per bag</span>
                <span>$18-28</span>
              </div>
              <div class="cost-item__row">
                <span>Lasts approximately</span>
                <span>3-5 weeks</span>
              </div>
              <div class="cost-item__row">
                <span>Monthly cost</span>
                <span>$15-37</span>
              </div>
              <div class="cost-item__row cost-item__row--total">
                <span>Annual cost</span>
                <span>$180-444</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <p class="cost__note">
          <strong>Plus:</strong> Fewer vet visits from respiratory issues, less cleaning time,
          and a more pleasant home environment. The value extends far beyond the price tag.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="cta-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Ready to Experience Premium?</h2>
      <p>
        Discover Purrify—the ultimate in premium cat litter innovation with biochar-powered
        odor control and eco-conscious ingredients.
      </p>
      <div class="cta-buttons">
        <a
          href="https://purrify.ca/products?utm_source=premiumcatlitter&utm_medium=why-premium"
          class="btn btn-primary btn-lg"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
        >
          Shop Purrify
        </a>
        <a href="/comparison" class="btn btn-secondary btn-lg">
          Compare Options
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style lang="scss">
  @use '../styles/variables' as *;
  @use '../styles/mixins' as *;

  .page-hero {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, $color-cream 0%, $color-champagne 100%);
    padding: $spacing-16 0 $spacing-20;
    text-align: center;

    @include lg {
      padding: $spacing-20 0 $spacing-24;
    }

    h1 {
      margin-top: $spacing-6;
      margin-bottom: $spacing-6;
    }

    &__subtitle {
      font-size: $font-size-lg;
      color: $color-text-secondary;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
  }

  .content-grid {
    display: grid;
    gap: $spacing-12;

    @include lg {
      grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr;
      gap: $spacing-16;
    }
  }

  .content-main {
    h2 {
      margin-bottom: $spacing-6;
    }

    h3 {
      margin-top: $spacing-10;
      margin-bottom: $spacing-4;
      color: $color-gold-dark;
    }

    p {
      font-size: $font-size-md;
      line-height: $line-height-relaxed;
    }
  }

  .content-sidebar {
    @include lg {
      position: sticky;
      top: 100px;
      height: fit-content;
    }
  }

  .info-card {
    background: $color-charcoal;
    border-radius: $border-radius-lg;
    padding: $spacing-8;
    color: $color-cream;

    &__icon {
      font-size: 32px;
      margin-bottom: $spacing-4;
    }

    h4 {
      color: $color-gold;
      margin-bottom: $spacing-6;
    }
  }

  .stats-list {
    @include flex-column;
    gap: $spacing-4;

    li {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      padding-bottom: $spacing-4;
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba($color-gold, 0.2);

      &:last-child {
        border-bottom: none;
        padding-bottom: 0;
      }
    }

    &__value {
      font-family: $font-heading;
      font-size: $font-size-2xl;
      font-weight: $font-weight-bold;
      color: $color-gold;
    }

    &__label {
      font-size: $font-size-sm;
      color: rgba($color-cream, 0.7);
    }
  }

  .health {
    background: $color-ivory;
  }

  .section-header {
    margin-bottom: $spacing-12;

    h2 {
      margin-bottom: $spacing-4;
    }
  }

  .section-subtitle {
    font-size: $font-size-lg;
    color: $color-text-secondary;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .benefits-grid {
    display: grid;
    gap: $spacing-6;

    @include sm {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }

    @include lg {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    }
  }

  .benefit-card {
    background: $color-white;
    border-radius: $border-radius-lg;
    padding: $spacing-6;
    text-align: center;
    box-shadow: $shadow-md;
    transition: all $transition-base;

    &:hover {
      transform: translateY(-4px);
      box-shadow: $shadow-lg;
    }

    &__icon {
      font-size: 40px;
      margin-bottom: $spacing-4;
    }

    h3 {
      font-size: $font-size-lg;
      margin-bottom: $spacing-3;
    }

    p {
      font-size: $font-size-sm;
      color: $color-text-secondary;
      margin: 0;
    }
  }

  .cost {
    background: $color-cream;

    &__content {
      max-width: 900px;
      margin: 0 auto;

      h2 {
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: $spacing-4;
      }

      > p {
        text-align: center;
        font-size: $font-size-lg;
        margin-bottom: $spacing-10;
      }
    }

    &__note {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: $font-size-md;
      color: $color-text-secondary;
      margin-top: $spacing-8;
    }
  }

  .cost-comparison {
    display: grid;
    gap: $spacing-6;

    @include md {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }
  }

  .cost-item {
    background: $color-white;
    border-radius: $border-radius-lg;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: $shadow-md;

    h4 {
      padding: $spacing-5;
      text-align: center;
      background: $color-slate;
      color: $color-cream;
      margin: 0;
    }

    &--premium {
      box-shadow: $shadow-gold;

      h4 {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, $color-gold, $color-gold-dark);
        color: $color-charcoal;
      }
    }

    &__details {
      padding: $spacing-5;
    }

    &__row {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      padding: $spacing-3 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba($color-charcoal, 0.1);
      font-size: $font-size-sm;

      &:last-child {
        border-bottom: none;
      }

      &--total {
        font-weight: $font-weight-bold;
        font-size: $font-size-md;
        color: $color-charcoal;
        padding-top: $spacing-4;
        margin-top: $spacing-2;
        border-top: 2px solid $color-gold;
        border-bottom: none;
      }
    }
  }

  .cta-section {
    background: $color-charcoal;
    padding: $spacing-16 0;
    text-align: center;

    h2 {
      color: $color-cream;
      margin-bottom: $spacing-4;
    }

    p {
      color: rgba($color-cream, 0.8);
      font-size: $font-size-lg;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto $spacing-8;
    }
  }

  .cta-buttons {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: $spacing-4;
    justify-content: center;
  }
</style>
